    <entry>
      <title>斐波拉契数列</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/29/FipolacciSequence/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/29/FipolacciSequence/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="总览"><a href="#总览" class="headerlink" title="总览"></a>总览</h1><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> i, j; <span class="comment">//声明两个变量</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> f1, f2, f3; <span class="comment">//声明三个变量</span></span><br><span class="line">　</span><br><span class="line">　f1 = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　f2 = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　f3 = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;i); <span class="comment">//获取用户输入的数字</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//判断用户输入的数字，是1输出1，是2输入1</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">if</span> (i == <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">　　<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"1"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (i == <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">　　<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"1"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">　　<span class="keyword">for</span> (j = <span class="number">3</span>; j &lt;= i; j++)</span><br><span class="line">　　&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　　　f1 = j;</span><br><span class="line">　　　f2 = f1;</span><br><span class="line">　　　f3 = f2;</span><br><span class="line">　　&#125;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, f3);</span><br><span class="line">　</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>输入6，输出8<br>输入9，输出34</p></blockquote><p>这里我们来逐步分析一下是怎么实现的</p><h2 id="第一步"><a href="#第一步" class="headerlink" title="第一步"></a>第一步</h2><p>斐波拉契数列的定义就是每个数字都是前两个数字之和，而前两个数字都是1，所以我们要先判断用户输入的是不是1或者2</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (i == <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"1"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (i == <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"1"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="第二步"><a href="#第二步" class="headerlink" title="第二步"></a>第二步</h2><p>利用for循环来实现每个数字都是前两个数字之和<br>我们需要声明三个变量<code>f1, f2, f3</code> ，类型定义为整数类型</p><blockquote><p>每次循环过后f2，f3都要互换数字，当然是让f2等于f1，让f3等于f2，又因为执行顺序，我们需要先让f3等于f2，之后再让f2等于f1</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">f3 = f2;</span><br><span class="line">f2 = f1;</span><br><span class="line">f1 = f2 + f3;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里可以看一下执行步骤</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//假设我们输入了5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>-&gt; i = <span class="number">5</span>，j = <span class="number">3</span> &lt; i 成立</span><br><span class="line">    f3 = <span class="number">1</span>; f2 = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    f1 = <span class="number">1</span> + <span class="number">1</span> = <span class="number">2</span>; j = <span class="number">4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>-&gt; i = <span class="number">5</span>，j = <span class="number">4</span> &lt; i 成立</span><br><span class="line">    f3 = <span class="number">1</span>; f2 = <span class="number">2</span>; </span><br><span class="line">    f1 = <span class="number">2</span> + <span class="number">1</span> = <span class="number">3</span>; j = <span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span>-&gt; i = <span class="number">5</span>; j = <span class="number">5</span> &lt;= i 成立</span><br><span class="line">    f3 = <span class="number">2</span>; f2 = <span class="number">3</span>; </span><br><span class="line">    f1 = <span class="number">3</span> + <span class="number">2</span> = <span class="number">5</span>; j = <span class="number">6</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">4</span>-&gt; i = <span class="number">5</span>; j = <span class="number">6</span> &gt;= i 不成立</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>从上面那个执行的流程可以很轻松的理解</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C语言 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>冒泡排序</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/29/BubbleSort/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/29/BubbleSort/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><a href="#zong">总览</a></li><li><a href="#zhi">执行流程</a></li></ul><a id="more"></a><h1 id="总览"><a href="#总览" class="headerlink" title="总览"></a><span id="zong">总览</span></h1><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">sort</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> * a, <span class="keyword">int</span> len)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> i, j, t;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">for</span> (i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; len<span class="number">-1</span>; ++i)</span><br><span class="line">　&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　　<span class="keyword">for</span> (j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; len<span class="number">-1</span>-i; ++j)</span><br><span class="line">　　&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　　　<span class="keyword">if</span> (a[j] &gt; a[j+<span class="number">1</span>])</span><br><span class="line">　　　&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　　　　t = a[j];</span><br><span class="line">　　　　a[j] = a[j+<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">　　　　a[j+<span class="number">1</span>] = t;</span><br><span class="line">　　　&#125;</span><br><span class="line">　　&#125;</span><br><span class="line">　&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> a[<span class="number">6</span>] = &#123;<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">21</span>, <span class="number">-9</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">2</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">　sort(a, <span class="number">6</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">6</span>; ++i)</span><br><span class="line">　&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　　<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d "</span>, a[i]);</span><br><span class="line">　&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>输出：-9 0 2 8 10 21</p></blockquote><h2 id="执行流程"><a href="#执行流程" class="headerlink" title="执行流程"></a><span id="zhi">执行流程</span></h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//第一次循环</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//1.1</span></span><br><span class="line">　i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">0</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">1</span>] 不成立, j = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//1.2</span></span><br><span class="line">　j = <span class="number">1</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; a[<span class="number">1</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">2</span>] 成立,</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">-9</span>, a[<span class="number">2</span>] = <span class="number">21</span>; j = <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//1.3</span></span><br><span class="line">　j = <span class="number">2</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; a[<span class="number">2</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">3</span>] 成立,</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">2</span>] = <span class="number">0</span>, a[<span class="number">3</span>] = <span class="number">21</span>; j = <span class="number">3</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//1.4</span></span><br><span class="line">　j = <span class="number">3</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; a[<span class="number">3</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">4</span>] 成立,</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">3</span>] = <span class="number">8</span>, a[<span class="number">4</span>] = <span class="number">21</span>; j = <span class="number">4</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//1.5</span></span><br><span class="line">　j = <span class="number">4</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; a[<span class="number">4</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">5</span>] 成立,</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">4</span>] = <span class="number">2</span>, a[<span class="number">5</span>] = <span class="number">21</span>; j = <span class="number">5</span>; i = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//第二次循环</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//2.1</span></span><br><span class="line">　i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">5</span>; j = <span class="number">0</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">4</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">0</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">1</span>] 成立,</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">-9</span>, a[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">10</span>; j = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="comment">//2.2</span></span><br><span class="line">　j = <span class="number">1</span>; j &lt; <span class="number">4</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">1</span>] &gt; a[<span class="number">2</span>] 成立,</span><br><span class="line">　a[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">0</span>, a[<span class="number">2</span>] = <span class="number">10</span>; j = <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>上面的流程只要仔细看了，再自己动手动脑写一遍就能懂了，也就不往下写了</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C语言 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>C语言结构体</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/29/C%20Struct/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/29/C%20Struct/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="结构体"><a href="#结构体" class="headerlink" title="结构体"></a>结构体</h1><ul><li><a href="#fuzhi">赋值和初始化</a></li><li><a href="#ruhe">如何提取出结构体变量中的每一个成员</a></li></ul><a id="more"></a><h1 id="赋值和初始化"><a href="#赋值和初始化" class="headerlink" title="赋值和初始化"></a><span id="fuzhi">赋值和初始化</span></h1><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> age;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">float</span> weight;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">char</span> sex;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span> <span class="title">st</span> = &#123;</span><span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">55.5</span>, <span class="string">'M'</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span> <span class="title">st1</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">　st1.age = <span class="number">18</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　st1.weight = <span class="number">55.5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　st1.sex = <span class="string">'M'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>想要构建结构体，只需要像上面那样，<code>struct 名称{};</code>而花括号里面输入想要的数据类型就可以了<br>如果想要赋值就可以在main函数中输入<code>struct 名称 变量名 = {};</code>就可以了</p><blockquote><ol><li>定义的同时可以整体赋值</li><li>定义时没有赋值，那么只能逐个赋值</li></ol></blockquote><h1 id="如何提取出结构体变量中的每一个成员"><a href="#如何提取出结构体变量中的每一个成员" class="headerlink" title="如何提取出结构体变量中的每一个成员"></a><span id="ruhe">如何提取出结构体变量中的每一个成员</span></h1><h2 id="1-结构体变量名-成员名"><a href="#1-结构体变量名-成员名" class="headerlink" title="1. 结构体变量名.成员名"></a>1. 结构体变量名.成员名</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> age;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">float</span> weight;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">char</span> sex;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span> <span class="title">st</span> = &#123;</span><span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">55.5</span>, <span class="string">'M'</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span> <span class="title">st1</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">　st1.age = <span class="number">18</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　st1.weight = <span class="number">55.5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　st1.sex = <span class="string">'M'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这个在赋值里面就已经出现过了，也就多说了。</p></blockquote><h2 id="2-指针变量名-gt-成员名"><a href="#2-指针变量名-gt-成员名" class="headerlink" title="2. 指针变量名-&gt;成员名"></a>2. 指针变量名-&gt;成员名</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">int</span> age;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">float</span> weight;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="keyword">char</span> sex;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span> <span class="title">st</span> = &#123;</span><span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">55.5</span>, <span class="string">'M'</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">　<span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Student</span> * <span class="title">pst</span> = &amp;<span class="title">st</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">　</span><br><span class="line">　pst-&gt;age = <span class="number">18</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　pst-&gt;weight = <span class="number">55.5</span>;</span><br><span class="line">　pst-&gt;sex = <span class="string">'M'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里的<code>pst-&gt;age</code>会被计算机内部转化为<code>(*指针变量名).成员名</code>来执行<br>如： pst-&gt;age 被转化成 (*pst).age</p><blockquote><p>pst-&gt;age 等价于 (*pst).age 等价于 st.age</p></blockquote><h1 id="杂记"><a href="#杂记" class="headerlink" title="杂记"></a>杂记</h1><h3 id="pst-gt-age的含义"><a href="#pst-gt-age的含义" class="headerlink" title="pst-&gt;age的含义"></a>pst-&gt;age的含义</h3><p>pst所指向的那个结构体变量中的age这个成员</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C语言 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Lua学习</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/18/LuaLearn/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/18/LuaLearn/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="这篇来开始看下Lua语言"><a href="#这篇来开始看下Lua语言" class="headerlink" title="这篇来开始看下Lua语言"></a>这篇来开始看下Lua语言</h1><a id="more"></a><blockquote><p>推荐使用软件:Androlua+</p></blockquote><h2 id="第一个Lua程序"><a href="#第一个Lua程序" class="headerlink" title="第一个Lua程序"></a>第一个Lua程序</h2><p>学习第一步我们来开始用Lua输出”Hello World”</p><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">"Hello world"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行之后，屏幕上会出现”Hello World”</p><h2 id="注释"><a href="#注释" class="headerlink" title="注释"></a>注释</h2><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">--单行注释</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">--[[</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">多行注释</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">]]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="字符串"><a href="#字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符串"></a>字符串</h2><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="string">"String"</span></span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="string">[[String]]</span></span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="string">[===[String]===]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="赋值"><a href="#赋值" class="headerlink" title="赋值"></a>赋值</h2><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="string">"Hello World"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">--或者多重赋值</span></span><br><span class="line">a,b = <span class="string">"Hello"</span>,<span class="string">"World"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">--又或者交换值</span></span><br><span class="line">a,b = b,a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="数值类型"><a href="#数值类型" class="headerlink" title="数值类型"></a>数值类型</h2><p>Lua中有8个基本类型分别为：</p><p>nil、boolean、number、string、userdata、function、thread和table。</p><p>1.nil<br>此类型只有一个值 nil。用于表示“空”值。全局变量默认为 nil，删除一个已经赋值的全局变量只需要将其赋值为 nil（对比 JavaScript，赋值 null 并不能完全删除对象的属性，属性还存在，值为 null）</p><p>2.boolean<br>此类型有两个值 true 和 false。在 Lua 中，false 和 nil 都表示条件假，其他值都表示条件真（区别于 C/C++ 等语言的是，0 是真）</p><p>3.number<br>双精浮点数（IEEE 754 标准），Lua 没有整数类型</p><p>4.string<br>你可以保存任意的二进制数据到字符串中（包括 0）。字符串中的字符是不可以改变的（需要改变时，你只能创建一个新的字符串）。获取字符串的长度，可以使用 # 操作符（长度操作符）。例如：print(#”hello”)。字符串可以使用单引号，也可以使用双引号包裹，对于多行的字符串还可以使用 [[ 和 ]] 包裹。字符串中可以使用转义字符，例如 \n \r 等。使用 [[ 和 ]] 包裹的字符串中的转义字符不会被转义</p><p>5.userdata<br>用于保存任意的 C 数据。userdata 只能支持赋值操作和比较测试</p><p>6.function<br>  函数是第一类值（first-class value），我们能够像使用其他变量一样的使用函数（函数能够保存在变量中，可以作为参数传递给函数）</p><p>  7.thread<br>  区别于我们常常说的系统级线程</p><p>  8.table<br>  被实现为关联数组（associative arrays），可以通过任何值来进行索引（nil 除外）。和全局变量一样，table 中未赋值的域为 nil，删除一个域只需要将其赋值为 nil（实际上，全局变量就是被放置在一个 table 中）</p><h2 id="Table-数组"><a href="#Table-数组" class="headerlink" title="Table(数组)"></a>Table(数组)</h2><p>table是lua唯一的数据结构。<br>table是lua中最重要的数据类型。<br>table类似于 python 中的字典。<br>table只能通过构造式来创建。其他语言提供的其他数据结构如array、list等等，lua都是通过table来实现的。<br>table非常实用，可以用在不同的情景下。最常用的方式就是把table当成其他语言的数组。</p><p>实例1:</p><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mytable = &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> index = <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">100</span> <span class="keyword">do</span></span><br><span class="line">  mytable[index] = <span class="built_in">math</span>.<span class="built_in">random</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1000</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>说明：<br>1.数组不必事先定义大小，可动态增长。<br>2.创建包含100个元素的table，每个元素随机赋1-1000之间的值。<br>3.可以通过mytable[x]访问任意元素，x表示索引。<br>4.索引从1开始。</p><p>实例2:</p><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tab = &#123; a = <span class="number">10</span>, b = <span class="number">20</span>, c = <span class="number">30</span>, d = <span class="string">'www.jb51.net'</span> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(tab[<span class="string">"a"</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>说明：<br>1.table 中的每项要求是 key = value 的形式。<br>2.key 只能是字符串， 这里的 a, b, c, d 都是字符串，但是不能加上引号。<br>3.通过 key 来访问 table 的值，这时候， a 必须加上引号。</p><p>实例3:</p><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tab = &#123; <span class="number">10</span>, s = <span class="string">'abc'</span>, <span class="number">11</span>, <span class="number">12</span>, <span class="number">13</span> &#125; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(tab[<span class="number">1</span>]) = <span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(tab[<span class="number">2</span>]) = <span class="number">11</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(tab[<span class="number">3</span>]) = <span class="number">12</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(tab[<span class="number">4</span>]) = <span class="number">13</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>说明：<br>1.数标从1开始。<br>2.省略key，会自动以1开始编号，并跳过设置过的key。</p><h2 id="比较操作符"><a href="#比较操作符" class="headerlink" title="比较操作符"></a>比较操作符</h2><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">--Lua</span> <span class="string">支持下列比较操作符：</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">==:</span> <span class="string">等于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">~=:</span> <span class="string">不等于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;:</span> <span class="string">小于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&gt;:</span> <span class="string">大于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;=:</span> <span class="string">小于等于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&gt;=:</span> <span class="string">大于等于</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">--这些操作的结果不是</span> <span class="literal">false</span><span class="string">就是</span> <span class="literal">true</span><span class="string">。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> lua </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Python爬虫</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/15/PythonSpider/"/>
