        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="这里是python爬虫的分享-◦˙▽˙◦"><a href="#这里是python爬虫的分享-◦˙▽˙◦" class="headerlink" title="这里是python爬虫的分享(◦˙▽˙◦)"></a>这里是python爬虫的分享(◦˙▽˙◦)</h1><a id="more"></a><h2 id="持续更新中…"><a href="#持续更新中…" class="headerlink" title="持续更新中….."></a>持续更新中…..</h2><blockquote><p>写代码的软件是:Pydroid3</p></blockquote><p>写代码之前我们务必安装相关模块，这里用到的三个模块，但其中两个python自带，所以安装一个就好了</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install requests</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完模块我们先新建一个文件</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#写个开头，先导入模块</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re <span class="comment">#正则表达式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time <span class="comment">#说下为什么要导入这个模块，因为这个网站是个人网站，非盈利性的，就不要那么狠心了，不然网站就404了</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建一个变量来获取网页内容<br>然后再print出来</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">response = requests.get(<span class="string">'https://www.vmgirls.com/12985.html'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(response.text) <span class="comment">#打印网页内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时候其实还不算完，我们先运行一下看看</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--这里很明显网站有反爬--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>403 Forbidden<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>403 Forbidden<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span>Nan<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们直接在这里加一段代码就可以了</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'User-Agent'</span>:<span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OSX10_14_2) AppleWebKit/537.36(KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/75.0.3770.100 Safari/537.36'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">response = requests.get(<span class="string">'https://www.vmgirls.com/12985.html'</span>,headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">print(response.text) <span class="comment">#打印网页内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>上面那个user-agent相当于我们的身份，我们拿这个身份来访问这个网页，如果不写这个的话，我们的默认身份就是python，这就相当于站在别人面前说我是爬虫<br>之后我们再print一下，就能够打印出来网页的内容了</p></blockquote><p>这个时候我们想想我们要的是什么?  我们要的是图片，所以我们要现在这个网页源代码里找到图片所在的位置<br>这里我用的是via浏览器，主要是里面有一个查询网页源代码的，总比我们这里写代码运行查看方便很多</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H99a90c853f874e2e8dc975cda521e9f3B.jpg" alt="源代码" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">源代码</div>            </figure><blockquote><p>向下翻翻很快就能找的到，我们可以看到，这些图片都是”&lt;a href=””alt=””title=””&gt;”</p></blockquote><p>看到这些规律之后就可以直接敲代码了，我这里用的是正规则表达式</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#pirnt(response.text)把这个改成下面那样方便点</span></span><br><span class="line">html = response.text</span><br><span class="line">urls = re.findall(<span class="string">'&lt;a href="(.*?)" alt=".*?" title=".*?"&gt;'</span>,html)</span><br><span class="line">print(urls)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hef59e43c5f874ed59a19e23f155bcfb54.jpg" alt="hiha" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">hiha</div>            </figure><p>可以看到已经成功了，我们把我们想要的都给读取出来了</p><p>这时候我们要进行的就是下载  在下面加上</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保存图片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> url <span class="keyword">in</span> urls: <span class="comment"># 请求上面的解析网页</span></span><br><span class="line">    time.sleep(<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="comment"># 让程序延迟2秒</span></span><br><span class="line">    file_name =url.split(<span class="string">'/'</span>)[<span class="number">-1</span>] <span class="comment"># split('/')【-1】是处理图片的名字</span></span><br><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> open(file_name, <span class="string">'wb'</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f: <span class="comment"># 打开一个文件,文件名是file_name</span></span><br><span class="line">        f.write(response.content)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>到这里就结束了,下面给大家全代码</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> re <span class="comment"># 正则表达式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'User-Agent'</span>:<span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OSX10_14_2) AppleWebKit/537.36(KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/75.0.3770.100 Safari/537.36'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">response = requests.get(<span class="string">'https://www.vmgirls.com/12985.html'</span>,headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">html = response.text</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解析网页</span></span><br><span class="line">urls = re.findall(<span class="string">'&lt;a href="(.*?)" alt=".*?" title=".*?"&gt;'</span>,html)</span><br><span class="line">print(urls)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 保存图片</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> url <span class="keyword">in</span> urls: <span class="comment"># 请求上面的解析网页</span></span><br><span class="line">    time.sleep(<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="comment"># 让程序延迟2秒</span></span><br><span class="line">    file_name =url.split(<span class="string">'/'</span>)[<span class="number">-1</span>] <span class="comment"># split('/')【-1】是处理图片的名字</span></span><br><span class="line">    response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">with</span> open(file_name, <span class="string">'wb'</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f: <span class="comment"># 打开一个文件,文件名是file_name</span></span><br><span class="line">        f.write(response.content)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
